ai-patthana17.14:0.2_0: Having given the immaterial states produced by the phenomena that are counterpart of
ai-patthana17.14:1.1_0: Unskillful lawless teaching doesn’t give rise to unprofitable roots.
ai-patthana17.14:1.1_1: ‘... for the sake of conditioned things.’ ...
ai-patthana17.14:1.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana17.14:2.1_0: Entering a wholesome quality doesn’t give rise to ineffacement, for the sake of a skillful teaching.
ai-patthana17.14:2.1_1: ‘... for the sake of conditioned things.’ ...
ai-patthana17.14:2.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana17.14:3.1_0: undetermined in this way, not cause or condition.
ai-patthana17.14:3.1_2: the five hindrances are not clear.
